  "sort_order": 5,
  "schema_version": 1,
  "cards": [
    {
      "id": "j-01",
      "deck_id": "jealousy",
      "text": "What's your earliest memory of jealousy?\n\nLong before this relationship. Maybe before any relationship.",
      "highlight_words": [
        "earliest memory"
      ],
      "type": "prompt",
      "intensity": 3,
      "who_starts": "partnerA",
      "is_sensitive": false,
      "can_skip": false,
      "register": "flexible",
      "context_beat_type": "banner",
      "context_beat_copy": "Jealousy has a memory. It's older than the two of you.",
      "back_copy": null,
      "is_gendered_card": false,
      "gendered_for": null,
      "sort_order": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "j-02",
      "deck_id": "jealousy",
      "text": "How was jealousy handled around you growing up?\n\nPunished? Romanticized? Hidden until it burst?",
      "highlight_words": [
        "Punished? Romanticized?"
      ],
      "type": "prompt",
      "intensity": 4,
      "who_starts": "partnerB",
      "is_sensitive": false,
      "can_skip": false,
      "register": "flexible",
      "context_beat_type": null,
      "context_beat_copy": null,
      "back_copy": null,
      "is_gendered_card": false,
      "gendered_for": null,
      "sort_order": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "j-03",
      "deck_id": "jealousy",
      "text": "Where does jealousy live in your body when it arrives?\n\nDon't explain it.\n\nLocate it.",
      "highlight_words": [
        "your body"
      ],
      "type": "bodyCheck",
      "intensity": 4,
      "who_starts": "both",
      "is_sensitive": false,
      "can_skip": false,
      "register": "flexible",
      "context_beat_type": null,
      "context_beat_copy": null,
      "back_copy": null,
      "is_gendered_card": false,
      "gendered_for": null,
      "sort_order": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "j-04",
      "deck_id": "jealousy",
      "text": "The last time it flared...\n\nWhat set it off?\n\nWhat was it pointing at underneath?",
      "highlight_words": [
        "underneath"
      ],
      "type": "prompt",
      "intensity": 5,
      "who_starts": "partnerA",
      "is_sensitive": false,
      "can_skip": false,
      "register": "flexible",
      "context_beat_type": "interstitial",
      "context_beat_copy": "Before this card:\n\nJealousy is a signal with a job. It shows up to point at something that matters to you. A need. A fear. A line.\n\nYou can read the signal without obeying it. Tonight you're just reading.",
      "back_copy": null,
      "is_gendered_card": false,
      "gendered_for": null,
      "sort_order": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "j-05",
      "deck_id": "jealousy",
      "text": "For him:\n\nHas the question ever visited you... could someone simply do this better?\n\nSay where comparison sneaks in for you, even when it arrives dressed as curiosity.\n\nThen, for her: name one thing about him nobody else could replace.",
      "highlight_words": [
        "replace"
      ],
      "type": "prompt",
      "intensity": 5,
      "who_starts": "both",
      "is_sensitive": false,
      "can_skip": false,
      "register": "flexible",
      "context_beat_type": null,
      "context_beat_copy": null,
      "back_copy": null,
      "is_gendered_card": true,
      "gendered_for": "mf",
      "sort_order": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "j-05f",
      "deck_id": "jealousy",
      "text": "Whichever of you carries the quieter fear of being outgrown:\n\nSay where comparison sneaks in for you, even when it arrives dressed as curiosity.\n\nThen the other: name one thing about them nobody else could replace.",
      "highlight_words": [
        "outgrown"
      ],
      "type": "prompt",
      "intensity": 5,
      "who_starts": "both",
      "is_sensitive": false,
      "can_skip": false,
      "register": "flexible",
      "context_beat_type": null,
      "context_beat_copy": null,
      "back_copy": null,
      "is_gendered_card": true,
      "gendered_for": "flexible",
      "sort_order": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "j-06",
      "deck_id": "jealousy",
      "text": "For her:\n\nWhat happens to your own feelings when you're busy managing someone else's?\n\nWhere have you shrunk your joy to keep the peace?\n\nSay one place you want that to stop.",
      "highlight_words": [
        "shrunk your joy"
      ],
      "type": "prompt",
      "intensity": 5,
      "who_starts": "both",
      "is_sensitive": false,
      "can_skip": false,
      "register": "flexible",
      "context_beat_type": null,
      "context_beat_copy": null,
      "back_copy": null,
      "is_gendered_card": true,
      "gendered_for": "mf",
      "sort_order": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "j-06f",
      "deck_id": "jealousy",
      "text": "Whichever of you dims your own excitement to protect the other:\n\nWhere has that been happening lately?\n\nSay one place you want it to stop.",
      "highlight_words": [
        "dims"
      ],
      "type": "prompt",
      "intensity": 5,
      "who_starts": "both",
      "is_sensitive": false,
      "can_skip": false,
      "register": "flexible",
      "context_beat_type": null,
      "context_beat_copy": null,
      "back_copy": null,
      "is_gendered_card": true,
      "gendered_for": "flexible",
      "sort_order": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "j-07",
      "deck_id": "jealousy",
      "text": "One word for your relationship with jealousy right now.",
      "highlight_words": [
        "One word"
      ],
      "type": "snapshot",
      "intensity": 4,
      "who_starts": "both",
      "is_sensitive": false,
      "can_skip": false,
      "register": "flexible",
      "context_beat_type": null,
      "context_beat_copy": null,
      "back_copy": null,
      "is_gendered_card": false,
      "gendered_for": null,
      "sort_order": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "j-08",
      "deck_id": "jealousy",
      "text": "What reassurance actually works on you?\n\nWords, touch, time, proof?\n\nWhich well-meant reassurance does nothing at all?",
      "highlight_words": [
        "actually works"
      ],
      "type": "prompt",
      "intensity": 6,
      "who_starts": "partnerB",
      "is_sensitive": false,
      "can_skip": false,
      "register": "anxious",
      "context_beat_type": null,
      "context_beat_copy": null,
      "back_copy": "Say the useless kind out loud too.\n\nNobody should keep spending effort where it never lands.",
      "is_gendered_card": false,
      "gendered_for": null,
      "sort_order": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "j-09",
      "deck_id": "jealousy",
      "text": "What if I came home lit up after a great date...\n\nWhat's the first thing you'd want me to do walking in the door?",
      "highlight_words": [
        "lit up"
      ],
      "type": "whatIf",
      "intensity": 5,
      "who_starts": "both",
      "is_sensitive": false,
      "can_skip": true,
      "register": "excited",
      "context_beat_type": null,
      "context_beat_copy": null,
      "back_copy": null,
      "is_gendered_card": false,
      "gendered_for": null,
      "sort_order": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "j-10",
      "deck_id": "jealousy",
      "text": "When have you felt something close to pride watching me light up for someone else?\n\nWhat made that moment safe enough for pride?\n\nWhat would it take to get more of them?",
      "highlight_words": [
        "pride"
      ],
      "type": "prompt",
      "intensity": 5,
      "who_starts": "partnerA",
      "is_sensitive": false,
      "can_skip": false,
      "register": "flexible",
      "context_beat_type": null,
      "context_beat_copy": null,
      "back_copy": null,
      "is_gendered_card": false,
      "gendered_for": null,
      "sort_order": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "j-11",
      "deck_id": "jealousy",
      "text": "The Working Signal.\n\nEach of you tells the other the exact sentence to say when jealousy shows up mid-experience.\n\nNow repeat each other's sentence back. Once. Out loud.",
      "highlight_words": [
        "exact sentence"
      ],
      "type": "closingRitual",
      "intensity": 3,
      "who_starts": "both",
      "is_sensitive": false,
      "can_skip": false,
      "register": "flexible",
      "context_beat_type": null,
      "context_beat_copy": null,
      "back_copy": null,
      "is_gendered_card": false,
      "gendered_for": null,
      "sort_order": 11
    }
  ]
}
